Template::Plugin::Filter::Minify::CSS is Copyright (C) 2009, Michael Schout.

WHAT IS THIS?

    This package contains the Template::Plugin::Filter::Minify::CSS.  This
    module is a filter for minifying css code during template processing.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other CPAN modules:

    Template 2.0
    CSS::Minifier

